# Tailwind v4

Entry: `@import "tailwindcss"` + `@config` in `app/globals.css` · tokens in `tailwind.config.ts`.

## Single sources

| Concern | Path |
|---------|------|
| Repeated class strings | `lib/tailwind.ts` (`TW_*`) — see also `16-dry.mdc` |
| Brand, shadows, gradients | `tailwind.config.ts` |
| Rich text | `rich-text` classes in `globals.css` — **not** `prose-*` |
| PT wrapper component | `components/content/RichTextBody.tsx` |
| Scroll/reveal utilities | `@utility` in globals; Reveal `.rv-*` |

## `TW_*` token map (`lib/tailwind.ts`)

Import before duplicating raw class strings. Compose with template literals: `` className={`bg-white ${TW_SECTION_PY}`} ``.

### Layout & containers

| Token | Use |
|-------|-----|
| `TW_CONTAINER` | Standard section width (`max-w-7xl`) |
| `TW_CONTAINER_HEADER` | Header inner shell |
| `TW_CONTAINER_HERO` | Homepage hero content area |
| `TW_CONTAINER_NARROW` | `max-w-3xl` prose, CTA, FAQ columns |
| `TW_CONTAINER_PROSE` | Donate quote block (`max-w-2xl`) |
| `TW_SECTION_PY` | Section vertical padding — pair with `bg-*` |
| `TW_PAGE_BODY` | CMS page body shell (`bg-slate-50/40`) |
| `TW_PAGE_HERO_PADDING` | `PageHeroHeader` inner padding |

Wider prose on lg screens: `` `${TW_CONTAINER_NARROW} lg:px-8` `` (about, donate, articles).

