## Do
- Utilities in `className` only — no CSS-in-JS
- Check `lib/tailwind.ts` before adding layout, section, or CTA classes
- `shrink-0` not `flex-shrink-0` · slash opacity `bg-dq-500/20`
- Theme shadows: `shadow-gold-*`, `shadow-nav`, `shadow-gold-subtle`, `shadow-focus-gold`
- RTL spacing → `03-rtl-urdu.mdc` (logical props; `start-*`/`end-*`, `ms-*`/`me-*`)
- Geometric centering (`left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2`) OK for symmetric pins (e.g. quote badge)

## Don't
- `@tailwindcss/typography` or `prose-*`
- Inline `style={{}}` for colors/gradients/shadows  
  OK: `--hero-delay`, LCP blur, `--nav-indent` CSS vars
- Raw hex for brand UI · duplicate arbitrary rgba shadows
- `@apply` except base/rich-text in `globals.css`
- Duplicate these — use tokens instead:
  - `max-w-7xl mx-auto px-*` → `TW_CONTAINER*`
  - `max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6` → `TW_CONTAINER_NARROW`
  - `py-16 sm:py-20` → `TW_SECTION_PY`
  - `w-5 h-px bg-dq-400` → `TW_EYEBROW_LINE`
  - `text-[13.5px] text-gray-500 leading-relaxed` under titles → `TW_PAGE_SUBTITLE`

## Brand exceptions
PayPal (`TW_PAYPAL_CTA`), WhatsApp float (`TW_WHATSAPP_FLOAT`) only.

